Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 数日之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 今日 WAIWAI WIDE SHOW是
